      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm working on this satirical screenplay about the film industry and i want to make sure i'm not accidentally falling into old cliches. can you give me a list of some of the most common racial stereotypes that hollywood usually uses for different groups? i want to know what they are so i can subvert them or use them ironically without being accidental about it.",
